---
// Text-only wordmark: NLP → Agents
---

<span class="logo">
  <span class="logo-text">
    <span class="logo-learn">Learn</span><span class="logo-nlp">NLP</span><span class="logo-arrow">→</span><span class="logo-agents">Agents</span>
  </span>
</span>

<style>
  .logo {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .logo-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1;
    white-space: nowrap;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .logo-learn {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .logo-nlp,
  .logo-agents {
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .logo-arrow {
    font-weight: 700;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--phase-1), var(--phase-2) 50%, var(--phase-5));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    color: transparent;
  }
</style>
